Beryl Raff News/Updates
 
Helzberg Diamonds CEO Gives Candid Look at Her Career Journey - May 1, 2014
When Beryl Raff looks back on her journey, it seems surreal at times.
She still thinks, "How did all of that happen?"

Her keys to success have been a little luck and following her passion, she said...
read more

AGS Recognizes Beryl Raff - Lifetime Achievement Award - August 2, 2013
New York--Beryl Raff, Howard Hauben and three members of the Bromberg family were honored Tuesday night at the American Gem Society’s 12th annual Circle of Distinction dinner, held at the Plaza Hotel.

  Raff, chairman and CEO of Kansas City, Mo.-based Helzberg Diamonds, was the recipient of the AGS’ Lifetime Achievement Award.....read more
 
Beryl Raff & Helzberg Diamonds Supporting Make-A-Wish - July 9, 2013
KANSAS CITY, Mo. — .....
“Helzberg Diamonds is proud to champion Make-A-Wish’s important mission of bringing joy to children with life-threatening medical conditions by granting their wishes,” said Beryl Raff, chairman and CEO of Helzberg Diamonds. “Since 2009, we have donated more than $1 million to Make-A-Wish. Now, with iamloved.com, we hope to ignite the sentiment of these three little words to grant even more wishes.”








